{"type":null,"faqId":14042,"title":"荣耀 X1 7.0 是否支持 microSD 卡升级？怎么操作？","answer":"<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">支持。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <br />\n</p>\n<p>\n  <hr />\n  <img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44759\" width=\"144\" height=\"43\" alt=\"\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" />\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">系统升级会清除荣耀</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">上的所有数据。建议您先备份数据后再升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">使用非授权的软件升级时，可能会造成升级失败、个人信息泄露等风险。建议您使用在线升级或下载官方发布的版本进行升级。</span>\n</p>\n<div style=\"border:none;padding:0cm 0cm 4.0pt 0cm;margin-left:3.0cm;\">\n  <p style=\"margin-left:14.2pt;\">\n    <span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"></span>\n  </p>\n</div>\n<p>\n  <hr />\n</p>\n请先从正规渠道下载升级包，并将升级包中的<span>&nbsp;<b>dload</b>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件夹拷贝到</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡根目录下。然后在主屏幕上点击<b>设置</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">常规设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机升级</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统软件更新</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本地升级</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会自动检测</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡里的升级包并进行升级。</span>\n<p>\n  <br />\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"figd0e309\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.2.6.2.4.1\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44760\" width=\"531\" height=\"627\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">升级过程中，屏幕上会显示升级进度及升级结果。</span>\n</p>","faqTypeId":173,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5702","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1406079375000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":1102,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"3","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"升级,SD卡,SD卡升级,卡升,刷机","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}